Package: lambdapply
Title: Apply R functions in AWS Lambda
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Liam", "Gilbey", , "liam.gilbey@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-9747-6608"))
Description: lambdapply aims to provide a familiar *apply syntax to R users, with
  an AWS lambda backend. This allows R users to scale R computation horizontally, and
  perform all iterations in a parallel fashion.
